text: "Olingi Nini" (Lingala for "What you want") is a song recorded by Congolese singer Gaz Mawete that was a massive huge success for his career and gain over 4.3 million views on YouTube. == See also == * KeBlack * Youssoupha * Fally Ipupa * Naza (rapper) == References == Category:Gaz Mawete songs Category:2018 songs
title: Olingi Nini
